By systematically examining relevant historical sources, texts, and literature, the course wish to guide students through a comprehensive understanding of key topics in Song society and culture. Specifically:
1) Students are supposed to understand the nature and core values of Song culture;
2) Students are supposed to have a basic sense of various regional societies in Song, Liao, Jin, and Yuan China;
3) Students are supposed to have some glances of the Song origins of late imperial China;
4) Students are supposed to enhance their aiblity in exploring historical sources concerning social and cultural histories

本科通過系統學習相關文獻、史料和前人論著，希望引導學生瞭解宋代社會與文化的核心議題。具體目標如下:
1) 掌握宋代文化要義以及核心價值;
2) 對宋代南、北社會形態(包括遼、金、元等)有基本之瞭解;
3) 通過瞭解宋代社會，加深對晚期帝制中國社會體制根源的認識；
4) 加深學生對社會史和文化史史料之運用能力。

